# Package.resolved is ALWAYS committed, never ignored — BOTH the package-root
# lockfile (next to Package.swift) and the app's Xcode workspace lockfile at
# App/GuessWho.xcodeproj/.../xcshareddata/swiftpm/Package.resolved. Committing
# both records the exact built dependency set at every commit hash. Do NOT add
# any Package.resolved ignore pattern here (not even a root-only `/Package.resolved`).
